birthmark.

15:00.750 --> 15:03.330
Like this.
Yeah. Just like that.

15:03.330 --> 15:07.250
You said this was gonna be
the best Christmas ever.

15:07.250 --> 15:11.750
Well, I don't want a tree
or wind-up dancing elves.

15:11.750 --> 15:13.500
Find him.

15:13.500 --> 15:16.660
Get Sam's dad out.

