You'd be surprised.

15:38.750 --> 15:41.950
Hey, hey, we're at party
in minus 50 minutes, people.

15:41.950 --> 15:43.540
Can I get some help here?

15:43.540 --> 15:45.950
Okay, Roger, Brooks
is in a crisis.

15:45.950 --> 15:47.700
He needs someone to
