15:47.700 --> 15:50.410
Well, can we listen
while he dices onions?

15:50.410 --> 15:53.040
It'll help mask his tears.

15:53.040 --> 15:53.950
Roger!

15:53.950 --> 15:55.620
That's probably the photo booth.

15:55.620 --> 15:58.250
He... By the way,
he left early today to do this.

15:58.250 --> 16:00.000
TRISH:
He did.

16:00.000 --> 16:04.000
