Plus zero, by the way.

16:06.250 --> 16:07.160
Change of plans. Do you mind

16:07.160 --> 16:09.330
if these guys
hang out here for a bit?

16:09.330 --> 16:10.160
Uh, Murtaugh,

16:10.160 --> 16:12.000
this is my best
friend Sam.

16:12.000 --> 16:14.040
Hey, Sam.
Do you dice vegetables?

16:14.040 --> 16:15.660
TRISH:
Honey. What?

16:15.660 --> 16:16.330
I'm serious.

16:16.330 --> 16:18.120
Maya, come on.
Bring your friend in.

16:18.120 --> 16:19.910
Come on.

16:19.910 --> 16:21.410
Thanks for helping my dad.

16:21.410 --> 16:23.160
You got it.

16:24.540 --> 16:27.950
Hey, Oscar's kid--
what did he mean?

16:27.950 --> 16:29.410
