16:29.410 --> 16:32.120
I can't. I got a party.
I can't just go.

16:32.120 --> 16:34.580
No problem. Why don't
you tell his kid, then?

16:34.580 --> 16:35.790
I'm sure he'll understand.

16:35.790 --> 16:39.620
All right. What's the lead?

16:40.330 --> 16:42.160
That's not a lead.

16:42.160 --> 16:45.200
That's a kid killing time
between French fries.

16:45.200 --> 16:46.330
