27:34.750 --> 27:37.210
Hey-hey!
RJ, listen, um...

27:37.210 --> 27:40.500
I know I got a little
carried away last night.

27:40.500 --> 27:42.920
May have scared you off
coming home.

27:42.920 --> 27:43.340
I hope not.

27:43.340 --> 27:47.670
I mean, you know, people book
the wrong flights all the time.

27:47.670 --> 27:49.460
I'm sure it's a common mistake.

